BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

a. [$cation1] sulfide is written as [`[$molecule1]`].

a. [$cation2] phosphide is written as [`[$molecule2]`].

a. calcium [$anion1] is written as [`[$molecule3]`].

a. magnesium [$anion2] is written as [`[$molecule2]`].




